summary: ATHENAS AI - A novel approach to creating a multifunctional AI application using Transformer Neural Network called Large Language Models (LLMs). Athenas AI is a new combination of conversational AI, Anonymous AI and web search skills in the quickly changing field of artificial intelligence and search technologies. Powered by cutting-edge language models, Athenas AI is not just an Ai tools, it is your intelligent learning companion, capable of answering complex queries across a myriad of domains and secure your privacy.
